data.name: sqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT ID, username, selected, proj_lot_id, pri_code, lot_class_code, lot_class_desc, plan_num, block_num, lot_num, pri_id, agreement_num, MasterAgreementNum, Purchaser_Code, Purchaser_Name, pri_name,deposit_amt, deposit_type, paid_todate, misc_supplier_code, misc_supplier_name, invoice_id FROM working_ld_LotSearch WHERE (username = @username) AND (selected = 1)
